    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 22. Nops cesari n. sp. Male 17 – 18. Nops quito n. sp. Male 19 – 20. Nyetnops juchuy n. sp. Male 21 – 22. 17. Tarsal claws I, lateral view. 18. Tarsal claws IV, lateral view. 19. Tarsal claws I, lateral view. 20. Tarsal claws IV, lateral view. 22. Tarsal claws I, lateral view. 22. Tarsal claws IV, lateral view." ;
